{"id": "QmYSC3EEC9ZgAtuHSvHZBJSVShJWZvFWD2JJH4kWWVEVH3", "title": "Add HirotoKai to the Wearables Curation Committee", "body": "> by 0x9982b469910c2ee2ea566dcfcc250cdd34056397 (MrEric)\n\n**Summary**\n\nWhile the wearables editor allows anyone to create wearables for Decentraland Avatars, all submissions must be reviewed and checked for technical issues or obvious infringements of Decentraland's content policies before they may be minted on Polygon and distributed. The [Wearables Curation Committee](https://docs.decentraland.org/decentraland/curation-committee/) was formed to help with this process.\n\nThere are currently only three individuals sitting on the Curation Committee, and the time and effort required to review submissions is exceeding their capacity.\n\nTo help guarantee that new wearables are reviewed and passed through the publication process in a timely manner, we need additional curation committee members.\n\n**The candidate**\n\nAfter the [call for nominations](https://forum.decentraland.org/t/wearables-curation-committee-member-nominations/2047),  HirotoKai was nominated:\n\n\"HK's dedication to the DCL Community, specifically with regards to wearables creation, has been immense and is not unnoticed. HK is active with creation solo and in-collaboration with others. Additionally, HK is consistently supporting others projects, addressing questions, and hosts wearable educational tutorials too. Much respect to HirotoKai!\"\n\n**Compensation**\n\nOn August 20th, 2021, the [DAO approved a proposal](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=268c9620-fc6b-11eb-bf2e-8bc0e796957b) to compensate each committee member with 50 MANA for every item they review.\n\nCommittee members are compensated per item reviewed (not hourly), and there are no hard time requirements. That being said, the current committee members are working between 10 and 20 hours per week. This workload is expected to change as the number of active committee members fluctuates.\n\n**Necessary qualifications**\n\nCuration Committee members must have previous experience that demonstrates their ability to provide high quality, technical feedback to creators. Specifically, committee members should have (at a minimum):\n\n*   Practical experience with 3D modeling and animation\n*   A full understanding of skin weighting\n*   A full understanding of the 3D asset pipeline for Decentraland wearables as documented here\n*   An understanding of the glTF asset pipeline\n*   A general understanding of the Decentraland platform and Decentraland's DAO\n*   A general understanding of blockchain transactions and layer 2 solutions\n\n**Should  HirotoKai be added to the Wearables Curation Committee?**\n\n- Yes\n- No\n- Invalid question/options\n\n\n**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=558fa9f0-1686-11ec-ac84-77607720a240)**", "choices": ["Yes", "No", "Invalid question/options"], "start": 1631752620, "end": 1632357420, "snapshot": "13233571", "state": "closed", "author": "0x5E23D08324f017d5425e59A2782C9ae27aCE0958", "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth", "name": "Decentraland"}, "votes": 34, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmVdcUXf9KVkvovEHQjhPrrwbJQqHFu8omGpmunurf3Pns", "voter": "0x5dA5F4c020f856aBdB168fd35c957D6006ba2edE", "created": 1632350346, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmQQb28nR99ffA6mfsHQEmuyaAVbQnueWso17W4fJiyif7", "voter": "0x7a5e56c9fb159FE942C724d929016313628e5661", "created": 1632263794, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmWPU6Cpbgjy53VHeEFaPLaaXhKyJS6iCX9DV6RiBBvCK9", "voter": "0x45208c10E922D932c0A638e7d8e92307fC73B40b", "created": 1632229494, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmY9m33PFMVo69QJNCfswqJPJ4yaAypuroVksqJGsbbS8i", "voter": "0x780909C4F1305E5953041E744B09E2F016180676", "created": 1632228800, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmTAAvdCniBbdcTcwJ6FqAzt7YSgg5S3753bEjzyfHLYRU", "voter": "0x86f